{"content": "I need to multiply 344\u2089 \u00d7 616\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n344\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 4 = 283\u2081\u2080\n\n616\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 486 + 9 + 6 = 501\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n283 \u00d7 501 = 141,783\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n141783 \u00f7 9 = 15753 r 6\n15753 \u00f7 9 = 1750 r 3\n1750 \u00f7 9 = 194 r 4\n194 \u00f7 9 = 21 r 5\n21 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 3\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **235436\u2089**\n\n235436", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 325}